%% Job lifecycle. See 03-capability-matrix.md, 08-event-and-workflow-architecture.md
stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Lead
  Lead --> Quoted: QuoteGenerated
  Quoted --> Booked: QuoteAccepted / DepositPaid
  Booked --> Scheduled: JobScheduled
  Scheduled --> Assigned: CrewAssigned / AssignmentSent
  Assigned --> Confirmed: AssignmentAccepted (link or verbal)
  Assigned --> Reassign: AssignmentDeclined
  Reassign --> Assigned
  Confirmed --> InProgress: WorkerClockedIn / JobStarted
  InProgress --> Changed: ChangeOrderCreated
  Changed --> InProgress: ChangeOrderApproved
  InProgress --> Delayed: JobDelayed
  Delayed --> InProgress
  InProgress --> Completed: JobCompleted (photos, clock-out)
  Completed --> Invoiced: InvoiceIssued
  Invoiced --> Paid: PaymentReceived
  Paid --> Reviewed: ReviewRequested
  Reviewed --> [*]
  Booked --> Cancelled
  Scheduled --> Cancelled
  Cancelled --> [*]
